{"title":"K-Nearest Neighbor","date":"2019-02-06T16:00:00.000Z","link":"2019/02/07/K-Nearest Neighbor","tags":["Machine Learning"],"categories":["Machine Learning"],"updated":"2019-10-25T07:26:44.474Z","content":"<h3 id=\"K-Nearest-Neighbor\">K-Nearest Neighbor<a href=\"2019/02/07/K-Nearest Neighbor#K-Nearest-Neighbor\"></a></h3><ol>\n<li>为了判断未知实例的类别，以所有已知类别的实例作为参考选择参数K</li>\n<li>计算未知实例与所有已知实例的距离</li>\n<li>选择最近K个已知实例</li>\n<li>根据少数服从多数的投票法则（majority-voting)，让未知实例归类为K个最邻近样本中最多数的类别</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"欧式距离\">欧式距离<a href=\"2019/02/07/K-Nearest Neighbor#欧式距离\"></a></h3><p>欧式距离也称为欧几里得距离具体如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week3/image/%E6%AC%A7%E5%BC%8F%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB1.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>其他距离衡量：余弦值（cos）,相关度（correlation）,曼哈顿距离（Manhattan distance）</p>\n<h4 id=\"k值的选取\">k值的选取<a href=\"2019/02/07/K-Nearest Neighbor#k值的选取\"></a></h4><p>k = 1 与未知分类相邻的一个点的类型</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week3/image/k%E5%80%BC1.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>k = 5 与未知分类相邻的5个点中，取相同点数最多的类型</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week3/image/k%E5%80%BC2.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>K的选取一般为奇数</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"算法缺点\">算法缺点<a href=\"2019/02/07/K-Nearest Neighbor#算法缺点\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week3/image/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%951.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<pre><code>- 算法的复杂度较高（需要比较所以已知实例与要分类的实例）\n\n- 当其样本分布不平衡时，比如其中一类样本过大（实例数量\n  过多）占主导的时候，新的未知实例容易被归类为这个主导\n  样本，因为这类样本实例的数量过大，但这个新的未知实例\n  实际并没有接近目标样本</code></pre>","prev":{"title":"SVM","link":"2019/02/10/SVM"},"next":{"title":"BP neural network","link":"2019/01/15/BP neural network"},"plink":"http://jccjd.top/2019/02/07/K-Nearest Neighbor/","copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://jccjd.top/2019/02/07/K-Nearest Neighbor/\" title=\"K-Nearest Neighbor\">http://jccjd.top/2019/02/07/K-Nearest Neighbor/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}